  %p The browser may render it correctly anyway, but it is invalid HTML and not all browsers may be as forgiving.

  %pre
    %code( data-trim="" )
      :preserve
        &lt;!-- BAD --&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          Chupa &lt;strong&gt;chups liquorice &lt;em&gt;marzipan gummi bears&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; stuff!
